{%- comment -%}
  SECTION: Main Collection Listview
DESCRIPTION:
  - Core collection product listing section that supports filtering, sorting,
    sidebar layout, pagination types (standard, load more, infinite scroll),
    and product display customization.
  - Displays collection products in a responsive grid with optional sidebar.
  - Additionally Background color option added for prodcut card image in section settings

  LOGIC OVERVIEW:
  If `section.settings.enable_sidebar` is true:
       → The layout splits into a sidebar (`custom-facets`) and main grid (`product-grid`).
  DEPENDENCIES:
  - CSS:
      • main-collection-listview.css
      • template-collection.css  
      • component-loading-overlay.css  
      • component-card.css, component-price.css, component-badge.css, component-rte.css  
      • section-main-product.css (conditional)
      • Need to add component-custom-product-view.css in theme.liquid - line no -394
  - JS:
      • load-more.js (for load_more/infinite_scroll)
      • facets.js (for filtering/sorting)
      • main-collection-listview-product-variant.js
      • layout-view.js → handles grid/list view functionality and toggle persistence.
  - Snippets:
      • facets.liquid / custom-facets.liquid
      • main-collection-listview-product-card.liquid - seperate product card for this component
      • main-collection-listview-variant-arrow - (product card) - custom-quick-view-icon.liquid , icon-info.liquid , quantity-input.liquid ,icon-minus.liquid , icon-minus.liquid, product-card-bulk.liquid
      • icon-spinner.liquid , load-more.liquid
      • section-margin.liquid
      • custom-list-view.liquid → list-view toggle icon.
      • custom-grid-view.liquid → grid-view toggle icon.
      • custom-quick-view-icon.liquid → quick view icon for mobile.
      
      Note: Its default section dupilication and code updated in custom-facets.liquid , component-card.css , component-facet.css , component-price.css
{%- endcomment -%}


{{ 'template-collection.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'component-loading-overlay.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{%- if settings.pagination_type == 'load_more' or settings.pagination_type == 'infinite_scroll' -%}
  <script src="{{ 'load-more.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>
{%- endif -%}
<script src="{{ 'layout-view.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>
<link rel="preload" href="{{ 'component-card.css' | asset_url }}" as="style" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'">
<link rel="preload" href="{{ 'component-price.css' | asset_url }}" as="style" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'">
<link rel="preload" href="{{ 'component-badge.css' | asset_url }}" as="style" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'">
<link rel="preload" href="{{ 'component-rte.css' | asset_url }}" as="style" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'">

<noscript>{{ 'component-card.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}</noscript>
<noscript>{{ 'component-price.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}</noscript>
<noscript>{{ 'component-badge.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}</noscript>
<noscript>{{ 'component-rte.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}</noscript>
{% comment %} <script src="{{ 'main-collection-listview-product-variant.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script> {% endcomment %}

{{ 'component-facets.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'component-offer.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{{ 'main-collection-listview.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- if section.settings.enable_filtering or section.settings.enable_sorting -%}
  {{ 'component-facets.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
